Bloomberg Markets with Carol Massar and Cory Johnson. GUEST: Felipe Hernandez Bloomberg Journalist Bloomberg Intelligence Discussing the markets and economy with Bloomberg Stocks Editor Dave Wilson, who also discusses his Chart of the Day "S&P 500 goes its own way after economic surprises peak."Email Dave at DWilson@bloomberg.net to sign up for the Chart.
